pageContext.claim: On Hillary Clinton: "So she had this massive advantage, she spent hundreds of millions of dollars more money than I spent. Hundreds of millions. ... Yeah. Or more, actually because we were $375 she was at $2.2 billion. But whatever.
pageContext.analysis: Trump exaggerates Clinton's spending. As of Dec. 9, 2016, Clinton's campaign committee had $565 million in total expenses and Trump's campaign committee had $322 million in expenses.
